'''Lynne Hale''' was Vice President of Publicity & Communications for [[Lucasfilm]] A thirty-five year veteran of the company, Hale helped to create and manage the return of the ''[[Star Wars]]'' saga to the public forefront, beginning with ''[[The Star Wars Trilogy Special Edition]]'' and continuing with the ''Star Wars'' [[prequel trilogy]] and the ''[[Star Wars: The Clone Wars]]'' television series. She retired at the end of [[2021]].

